       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. PROG04.

       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
       FILE-CONTROL.
           SELECT ARQ-CONTAS ASSIGN TO UT-S-ENTRADA.
           SELECT ARQ-SAIDA  ASSIGN TO UT-S-SAIDA.

       DATA DIVISION.
       FILE SECTION.
       FD  ARQ-CONTAS LABEL RECORDS STANDARD
           BLOCK CONTAINS 0 RECORDS.
       01  REG-CONTA.
           05 NUM-CONTA    PIC 9(08).
           05 NOME-CLIENTE PIC A(30).
           05 AGENCIA      PIC 9(04).
           05 TIPO-CONTA   PIC A(01).
           05 SALDO        PIC S9(09)V99.

       FD  ARQ-SAIDA LABEL RECORDS STANDARD
           BLOCK CONTAINS 0 RECORDS.
       01  REG-SAIDA PIC X(132).

       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  WS-VARIAVEIS.
           05 WS-FIM-ARQUIVO PIC X(01) VALUE 'N'.
           05 WS-TOT-CONTAS  PIC 9(04) VALUE ZEROS.
           05 WS-TOT-SALDO   PIC S9(13)V99 VALUE ZEROS.
           05 WS-AG-ANTERIOR PIC 9(04) VALUE ZEROS.
           05 WS-SUB-SALDO   PIC S9(13)V99 VALUE ZEROS.

       01  WS-LINHA-DETALHE.
           05 FILLER         PIC X(04) VALUE 'AG: '.
           05 WS-DET-AG      PIC 9(04).
           05 FILLER         PIC X(08) VALUE ' | C/C: '.
           05 WS-DET-CC      PIC 9(08).
           05 FILLER         PIC X(09) VALUE ' | NOME: '.
           05 WS-DET-NOME    PIC X(30).
           05 FILLER         PIC X(11) VALUE ' | SALDO: '.
           05 WS-DET-SALDO   PIC -ZZZ,ZZZ,ZZZ,ZZ9.99.
           05 FILLER         PIC X(38) VALUE SPACES.

       01  WS-LINHA-SUBTOTAL.
           05 FILLER         PIC X(25) VALUE 'SUBTOTAL SALDO AGENCIA: '.
           05 WS-SUB-VAL     PIC -ZZZ,ZZZ,ZZZ,ZZ9.99.
           05 FILLER         PIC X(90) VALUE SPACES.

       01  WS-LINHA-TOTAL.
           05 FILLER         PIC X(30) VALUE 'SALDO TOTAL: '.
           05 WS-TOT-S-OUT   PIC -ZZZ,ZZZ,ZZZ,ZZ9.99.
           05 FILLER         PIC X(84) VALUE SPACES.

       01  WS-TRACINHOS      PIC X(132) VALUE ALL '-'.

       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       1000-PRINCIPAL.
           OPEN INPUT ARQ-CONTAS OUTPUT ARQ-SAIDA.
           PERFORM 2000-LER-REGISTRO.
           IF WS-FIM-ARQUIVO = 'N'
              MOVE AGENCIA TO WS-AG-ANTERIOR.
           PERFORM 3000-PROCESSAR UNTIL WS-FIM-ARQUIVO = 'S'.
           PERFORM 5000-GRAVA-SUBTOTAL.
           PERFORM 4000-FINALIZAR.
           CLOSE ARQ-CONTAS ARQ-SAIDA.
           STOP RUN.

       2000-LER-REGISTRO.
           READ ARQ-CONTAS AT END MOVE 'S' TO WS-FIM-ARQUIVO.

       3000-PROCESSAR.
           IF AGENCIA NOT = WS-AG-ANTERIOR
              PERFORM 5000-GRAVA-SUBTOTAL
              MOVE AGENCIA TO WS-AG-ANTERIOR.
           ADD 1 TO WS-TOT-CONTAS.
           ADD SALDO TO WS-TOT-SALDO.
           ADD SALDO TO WS-SUB-SALDO.
           MOVE AGENCIA      TO WS-DET-AG.
           MOVE NUM-CONTA    TO WS-DET-CC.
           MOVE NOME-CLIENTE TO WS-DET-NOME.
           MOVE SALDO        TO WS-DET-SALDO.
           WRITE REG-SAIDA FROM WS-LINHA-DETALHE.
           PERFORM 2000-LER-REGISTRO.

       5000-GRAVA-SUBTOTAL.
           MOVE WS-SUB-SALDO TO WS-SUB-VAL.
           WRITE REG-SAIDA FROM WS-LINHA-SUBTOTAL.
           WRITE REG-SAIDA FROM WS-TRACINHOS.
           MOVE ZEROS TO WS-SUB-SALDO.

       4000-FINALIZAR.
           MOVE WS-TOT-SALDO TO WS-TOT-S-OUT.
           WRITE REG-SAIDA FROM WS-LINHA-TOTAL.